source:
I am from a farmer family in Vietnam - a very small country in Southeast Asia. I joined the cryptocurrency market in an effort to ease the burden on my parents. The day I deposited Sencha LPs is the last day of the Lunar New Year (Tet holiday) in my country. That money was my only remaining saving after I had paid all the debts for my family with the hope that after the holiday I can withdraw this money to pay the tuition fee for my brother. Sadly, All gone, you know :( 
I know that this money for everybody will not be that much but to me, it was all my savings in 2021. The value in $ is small but in VND it is a lot. I am extremely happy and moved to tears when hearing that I can have even a small chance to be refunded. I hope you can understand my difficulty.
Thanks so much in advance for your goodness. I am looking forward to receiving back my money.
